creator: John Kendrick Bangs
description:
LibriVox recording of Jack and the Check book by John Kendrick Bangs.
Read in English by Cate Barratt
Bangs is in top form in his version of this small collection of timeless fairy tales. If you don't immediately recognize Jack and the Check Book, Puss, the Promoter, and the Golden Fleece, don't worry, you soon will. - Summary by Cate Barratt
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

M4B Format Available
subject: librivox; audiobooks;short stories; humourous fiction
